data.description: Your Dream Riverfront Property Awaits! Nestled in serene seclusion along the picturesque Umpqua River, this breathtaking riverfront home offers a retreat for those seeking the perfect blend of tranquility and modern comforts. Embrace the open, airy ambience of high vaulted ceilings, with thoughtfully designed windows that bathe the living spaces in an inviting glow. Private and spacious primary suite conveniently located on the main floor. Ample RV and Boat parking featuring hookups, and a large tool shed. Fully finished basement with separate exterior access and garage, offering abundant space for hobbies, storage, or to be customized to your unique needs. Enjoy your morning coffee while relishing gorgeous views from the brand new wraparound deck, where the river becomes an extension of your backyard. Experience the joy of fishing and rafting just steps away from your back yard, creating endless opportunities for outdoor adventure. Don?t miss your chance! With its exceptional features and ambience that captures the essence of riverside living, this home is a must see for anyone searching for their own slice of paradise. Your Riverfront Oasis Awaits - Shown by appointment only. Recent appraisal on file - available by request. Schedule your showing today!
